{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fb8d181bea","title":"毛泽东主席接见缅共柯生（德钦巴登顶）等谈话记录","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b95f5c5a3d","index":0,"year":1967,"month":11,"day":26,"articleId":"fb8d181bea"}],"tags":[{"id":"29143cbd32","name":"无产阶级国际主义","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"4f45e132a9","name":"贵州文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"57eea82497","name":"康生","type":"人物"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"b3c50bb47c","name":"刘宁一","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"eb87a9588f","name":"四川文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"jimi","name":"机密档案中新发现的毛泽东讲话","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"epub","author":"宋永毅","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/机密档案中新发现的毛泽东讲话.epub"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"jimi":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4255e135b1","type":"paragraph","text":"（未经本人审阅）","index":0,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"512455d33b","type":"paragraph","text":"【德钦巴登顶（1914-1997）， 时任缅甸共产党副主席，1975年后为主席。1964年 9月, 缅共中央制定了“赢得战争，夺取政权”的革命路线，这是缅共历史上的一个重要转折点。1968年初，缅共又在缅东北开辟了新的革命根据地，并建立了依靠贫雇农、联合中农的基层人民民主政权。1968年9月24日，德钦丹东主席遇害后，由德钦巴登顶为副主席。柯生为他在中国国内的化名。】","index":1,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"90efd2bc52","type":"paragraph","text":"时　间：1967年11月26日17时30分至18时55分","index":2,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"abf69aa14b","type":"paragraph","text":"地　点：人民大会堂湖南厅","index":3,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"a75254689b","type":"paragraph","text":"参加人：","index":4,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"90725613e0","type":"paragraph","text":"缅方：柯明、罗线、何高、杨光、古方、吴明、甘底、赵明、赵云","index":5,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"dcd68140fa","type":"paragraph","text":"中方：周恩来、陈伯达、康生、江青、戚本禹、姚文元、刘宁一、杨成武、李天佑、徐其孝、申健、成学俞、苑化冰、陈杰夫、王阳","index":6,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"4972584168","type":"paragraph","text":"翻　译：陈川戈","index":7,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"07afd1b254","type":"paragraph","text":"速　记：吕辉祥","index":8,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"c8ec23ac34","type":"paragraph","text":"（在谈话之前，毛主席接见了来到北京的缅共和罗线部队代表134人并照相。）","index":9,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"9642865733","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席（以下简称主席）：你们到北京有多久了？","index":10,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"1f8c4d608d","type":"paragraph","text":"柯生（以下简称柯）：同志们到北京大概一个多星期了。他们（指何高、杨光等）来得比较早，一个多月了。","index":11,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"d20c986b97","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：那些同志到过北京吗？","index":12,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"9c33296e21","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：没有。他们这一次能见到毛主席，感到非常高兴，对他们是一个很大的鼓舞。","index":13,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"323ce5f5ca","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：到中国来的同志一共有多少人？","index":14,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"148fe331a4","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：现在第一批要出发的是330人，后面还有人。","index":15,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"eceeb9c0f7","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：你们来中国多少年了？","index":16,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"21b7cbf725","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：17年了。","index":17,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"6bf5529809","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：（向柯明）你也来了17年了？","index":18,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"8ae854b68f","type":"paragraph","text":"柯明（以下简称明）：我来中国有两年多了。","index":19,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"6864df8999","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：我们在中国17年不能回到缅甸去，这次主席的路线取得了胜利，我们能回去感到非常高兴。（这时主席笑了）","index":20,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"db02712368","type":"paragraph","text":"明：我们在农村坚持了十几年，对毛主席非常敬仰。因为有毛主席，所以我们能坚持下来。请毛主席给我签一个字，留着纪念。（主席在柯明的《毛主席语录》上签字）","index":21,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"ce74cea871","type":"paragraph","text":"我现在走了。非常感谢主席。","index":22,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"3df3735fb4","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：这不需要感谢。","index":23,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"d8b7369670","type":"paragraph","text":"（这时柯明退席）","index":24,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"3b48f1f576","type":"paragraph","text":"（向柯生）我跟你见过几次了？","index":25,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"1526bb3286","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：四次。1963年缅甸和谈时一次，最后一次是今年国庆。","index":26,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"72553ec5fa","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：63年到现在已经5年了。那些同志回去都好吗？","index":27,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"bbad81f220","type":"paragraph","text":"（这时，罗线等四人进来，参加了谈话）","index":28,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"9377972120","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：很好。这是罗线同志、甘底同志、赵明同志、赵云同志。","index":29,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"e0d703fb18","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：（对罗线）你到中国十几年了，一直没有看见你。","index":30,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"f481017243","type":"paragraph","text":"罗线（以下简称罗）：见到主席非常高兴。","index":31,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"c04667f421","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：你一直在四川还是贵州？","index":32,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"558314806c","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：住在贵阳。","index":33,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"df2aefc0d0","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：看样子你并不怎么老嘛。","index":34,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"9d6bfbfe88","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：45岁了。还可以打30年仗。","index":35,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"001334da77","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：可以。45、55、65、75，可以。","index":36,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"656a75c2c8","type":"paragraph","text":"重要的是要在斗争中学习，训练班也可以办一点。真正的学习是打仗。如果不去打仗，学习不到什么东西。单是课堂上学军事、学政治我看懂的还是少。","index":37,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"5687533f69","type":"paragraph","text":"你们在中国学习这些东西，回去切不可照抄。要按照你们的情况办。","index":38,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"91bb825003","type":"paragraph","text":"你们跟泰国有接触吗？","index":39,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"2a1271e1c7","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：跟泰国南部有接触，北部没有。","index":40,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"eeb0c48f53","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：（对罗线）在你们国家，你这个民族算少数民族。你这个民族有多少人？","index":41,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"01adc78ff8","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：20万。","index":42,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"8f46ef3c3b","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：还有其他少数民族？","index":43,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"2e351a7f49","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：很多，有100多个民族。缅甸人口的45%是少数民族。","index":44,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"ad73e77ba7","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：少数民族政策是一项重要的政策。","index":45,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"bddc29a99a","type":"paragraph","text":"你们全国有多少人口？","index":46,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"a46ab0e560","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：2500万。","index":47,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"106d94d5c9","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：面积多大？","index":48,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"44be432137","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：262000平方英里。","index":49,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"473a884ae0","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：是一个大国嘛。同越南差不多，比它大一点。","index":50,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"6153b02dde","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：比越南大一些。缅甸的面积比罗马尼亚、南斯拉夫、阿尔巴尼亚三个国家加起来还大。","index":51,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"744024d978","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：26万平方英里，合60万平方公里，跟四川差不多大。","index":52,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"3978b26824","type":"paragraph","text":"你们都在中国有十几年了吗？","index":53,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"f3278a79f3","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：何高同志17年，杨光同志17年，古方同志15年，罗线同志18年。","index":54,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"ca711ea1c6","type":"paragraph","text":"刘、邓路线的结果，使我们正是青春的时候在中国度过了，不过为时不晚，还可以打仗。","index":55,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"58ba65ca6b","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：为时不晚，还可以打仗。你们这个仗是哪一年打起的？","index":56,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"46ef59e72e","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：1948年。","index":57,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"cd7ee71d79","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：快20年了。","index":58,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"1eff75c844","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：明年3月28日就整整20年了。","index":59,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"d68174c7f3","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：这是一种情况，是两个帝国主义世界大战之间、处于世界和平时期的一种战争。","index":60,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"d90bd0df97","type":"paragraph","text":"中国的革命你们知道，是第一次世界大战以后才发生的。1918年到1925年7年以后才有北伐战争。1927年蒋介石叛变。共产党跟国民党打仗，是从1927年开始的，一直到第二次世界大战以后。时间拖得很长。","index":61,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"0090abf65b","type":"paragraph","text":"世界上还要打世界大战的。但是你们不能等它。","index":62,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"1013153e87","type":"paragraph","text":"你们估计奈温有没有可能把外国军队引进来？","index":63,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"061db50b53","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：1965年我党主席说过，如果奈温打不过，他可能把美军引进缅甸。我看目前这个可能性不太大。","index":64,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"640011b549","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：这个可能性不太大。","index":65,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"90c9668a29","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：引进美军，我们正希望他这样做。现在看来，美军运到南越很多，要再运到缅甸来有困难。我们得到一个消息，英国人告诉奈温：你不要把希望寄托在美军帮助你们缅甸上。","index":66,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"988f582100","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：但是他们要灭亡的时候，还是要把外国军队引进来的。","index":67,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"013c1d3bb9","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：对，我们党已经在思想上做好了准备。","index":68,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"4cb68bf965","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：引进来也不是一件坏事。比如，泰国就驻有美军。有帝国主义，也有封建主义。泰国共产党搞得好，很有前途，很有希望。","index":69,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"128f7e4b03","type":"paragraph","text":"你们这些同志过去在乡村里的人多，还是在城市里的人多？","index":70,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"61d8577414","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：大部分都是农村的。","index":71,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"803b906a43","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：在农村上过学吗？","index":72,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"d4994be257","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：有些上过学。大部分同志到了中国以后才学文化。缅文，景颇文都是到中国以后学习的。","index":73,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"648f7b2efc","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：有这样的教科书吗？","index":74,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"e119c4f367","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：用旧的教科书。","index":75,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"b67b781026","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：也可以自己编嘛。你们的家属、小孩现在教什么？","index":76,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"93e46bf175","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：现在在中国的这些家属，准备将来参加缅甸革命，因此他们现在学习五种东西，即医务、电台、修理枪支、文工团、造炸药。","index":77,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"9787a907e8","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：我说的是小孩。","index":78,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"c7da4e412d","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：小孩也学习。","index":79,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"37ff0471fc","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：他们是学习缅甸文吗？","index":80,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"179c509d11","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：是学习缅甸文。","index":81,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"50fe99d9c1","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：学习缅甸文才好。（对罗线）你们也要学习你们少数民族的文字。你们有自己的书吗？","index":82,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"bad2c21511","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：有。","index":83,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"41c838bf6b","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：你们懂不懂缅甸文？","index":84,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"1f6c2bc2d8","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：大部分都可以讲缅语。","index":85,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"38406abdf3","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：这个条件好。","index":86,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"d5f91a7c50","type":"paragraph","text":"他们单独有学校吗？","index":87,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"ea95cc75bc","type":"paragraph","text":"周恩来（以下简称周）：现在开始单独搞了。","index":88,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"2e9f8167fc","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：不是跟我们的孩子们在一起读书？","index":89,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"a7546f660d","type":"paragraph","text":"周：不是。","index":90,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"18c7f5be7f","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：在工厂还是在农村？","index":91,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"fa7af6b6d8","type":"paragraph","text":"周：有的在农村，有的在工厂。","index":92,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"29b409f475","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：不是搞了什么工厂吗？","index":93,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"b9f0c74532","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：大部分在工厂，有一个水银工厂。","index":94,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"d0add297fe","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：这个厂子在贵州什么地方？","index":95,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"f350eee7b0","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：黄平。","index":96,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"799d5e9816","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：是红军经过的地方吗？","index":97,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"014ccb90be","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：是。","index":98,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"5e0c3e3cf3","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：那是1934年底，1935年春，那时正是我们很困难的时候，我们党内犯了错误，即王明路线。","index":99,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"46a8610bd7","type":"paragraph","text":"听说你们党内拥护刘少奇的盛一本集团的几个人都跑掉了？","index":100,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"7311860f6c","type":"paragraph","text":"康生（以下简称康）：跑了一个。","index":101,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"f06cac9524","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：不止跑一个。","index":102,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"c6ceb53466","type":"paragraph","text":"康：还有两个没有跑。现在他们叫巴丁-泰路线。一个叫巴丁，另一个叫郭泰。","index":103,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"4356f64527","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：在国内有两个，在中国还有一个，即王江。","index":104,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"509b5ea645","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：这个名字我熟悉。这个人我见过没有？","index":105,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"99f22dc5ab","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：见过。","index":106,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"4d62edad44","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：他写信给奈温想投降。只要不投降，人数少并不要紧。（问罗线）你过来的时候是多少人？","index":107,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"4a086c73ae","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：大概将近400人。","index":108,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"521dbea146","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：现在还有多少人？","index":109,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"80394fb52d","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：347人。","index":110,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"8f14e54afc","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：为什么减少了呢？","index":111,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"adb5ef0ebf","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：有的死亡了，有的回家了。","index":112,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"b69588a4ed","type":"paragraph","text":"何高：回家的人是这种情况：他们本来是住在中国境内的，后来跑到缅甸参加他们的部队，进入中国后就送他们回家了。","index":113,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"948b992e81","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：他们爱和平，不爱战争。","index":114,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"33b1122b72","type":"paragraph","text":"康：现在增加的小孩有多少？","index":115,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"b91de3f1f7","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：480多人，将近500。","index":116,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"78ff20312d","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：你们回国，你们的家属放心吗？","index":117,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"f77634fbf1","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：放心。","index":118,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"4950150de9","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：放心。我们还准备做一些工作，有条件的、政治好的要动员他们参加缅甸革命。","index":119,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"b5e07e7657","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：好。要做些工作。缅甸有工业吗？","index":120,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"9f2c996750","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：有一点工业。","index":121,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"07fee2767a","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：有农业、工业、交通、开采石油。","index":122,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"b7d1131afc","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：是的。","index":123,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"c5789894ab","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：你们的同志主要住在哪里？","index":124,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"246347972e","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：四川。","index":125,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"e335ff84e5","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：现在集中在什么地方？","index":126,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"ef79baf601","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：大部分都到怒江坝，靠近保山那个地方。","index":127,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"19bc7cd3be","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：你们到中国十几年了，看样子年纪不很大嘛。","index":128,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"8a75e133f0","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：赵明同志年纪最轻，今年35岁。赵明同志、赵云同志刚到中国的时候还是小孩。","index":129,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"6549bb2fce","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：35岁，住了17年，到中国时是18岁。","index":130,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"d5e6f9f162","type":"paragraph","text":"你今年四十几岁？","index":131,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"6e12237ac8","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：45。","index":132,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"26932c9296","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：（问柯生）你跟他差不多？","index":133,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"c5f9b2490c","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：我比他大，今年54。","index":134,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"7f2b59d6af","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：你们大部分的困难还是武器和医药。武器你们主要还是向奈温要。","index":135,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"b0fd1ab98d","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：（对罗线）你要记住一条，向敌人要武器。","index":136,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"b837743825","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：向主席保证。","index":137,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"e171862d75","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：从敌人手里夺武器，这才有保证。你们有的地方根本没有办法靠外国，如勃固山区。","index":138,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"351d4c7905","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：是的，只能向敌人要。","index":139,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"bcf6f05b83","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：我并不是说，你们向我们要武器我们不给你们。这是个辅助条件。基本的条件要靠你们自己向敌人夺取武器。","index":140,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"7ceb53572a","type":"paragraph","text":"有些武器也可以自己制造，像地雷、手榴弹之类。自己也可办修理厂，修理枪支。","index":141,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"ef99af773f","type":"paragraph","text":"制造武器、弹药，修理枪支都不困难，这不是一个基本的问题。基本的问题是政治问题。军事不是主要的，政治是主要的。第一条，这个仗要不要打？一个要打，一个不要打。你们现在有那么一些人跑到奈温那里去，他们就是不要打的嘛。过去有这样的人，今后还会有这样的人。","index":142,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"0f454607be","type":"paragraph","text":"第二条，就是群众的问题。依靠群众，还是脱离群众？依靠群众总不会失败的，可以持久。","index":143,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"ffd44c8c69","type":"paragraph","text":"在根据地办学校，要学会政治、学会军事、学会打仗，学会其他的工作。","index":144,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"d1e1fe1069","type":"paragraph","text":"他们（指赵明、赵云）来的时候虽然小，那时也有些经验嘛。","index":145,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"6e47e5a5e0","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：是有一点经验。","index":146,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"36f9a7e957","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：（问罗线）这边是你的部队？","index":147,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"e24c5c7034","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：是的，他们（指赵明等）是快到中国边境时才参加部队的，参加部队3个月以后就到中国境内来了。","index":148,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"b38028aeae","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：中国境内也有景颇族嘛。有没有参加你们队伍的？","index":149,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"bdc2dd750e","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：有，现在已经送他们回家了。","index":150,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"a9201a4106","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：何必送他们回去呢？你们需要的时候还可以动员一批人参加你的部队。","index":151,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"7f32e2da6b","type":"paragraph","text":"景颇族在中国有多少？","index":152,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"3facd4d35d","type":"paragraph","text":"周：8万多。","index":153,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"657f27f905","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：都靠近你们边界，可以作为你们的后方嘛。","index":154,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"b27b1b248b","type":"paragraph","text":"缅族跟别的民族有什么联系没有？比如同泰族、同马来亚民族、同印度的民族有没有联系？你们是一个独立的民族？","index":155,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"44cab58c7d","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：关于缅甸民族的起源还有争论。一种认为缅甸民族是从西藏过去的，另一种认为是从甘肃过去的。缅族处在两大国之间，一个是印度，一个是中国。两国的文化对缅甸都有影响，但是缅族能独立生存下来。缅族跟马来族没有什么关系，跟泰国的泰族经常打仗。","index":156,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"c874a10312","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：跟印度的民族有没有什么关系？","index":157,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"42ad44194f","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：也没有。","index":158,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"194e6368e3","type":"paragraph","text":"康：缅语语法跟日语语法一样。","index":159,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"32fe5615ea","type":"paragraph","text":"周：缅文是不是接近藏文？","index":160,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"b8a1e38c48","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：跟藏文没有什么关系。","index":161,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"d3eced6be4","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：中国民族是从哪里来的，我也搞不清楚。","index":162,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"667a83804c","type":"paragraph","text":"周：现在也说法不一，有的认为，北方人是从西北来的，南方广东、福建是从南洋来的。","index":163,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"2105e5e539","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：从两条路来的。","index":164,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"e3afa802f0","type":"paragraph","text":"印度恐怕是从西方来的，看样子就像西方人。那加族的武装呢？","index":165,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"366774570d","type":"paragraph","text":"徐其孝（以下简称徐）：已经出去了。","index":166,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"b12b57184c","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：现在到哪里了？","index":167,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"839471b3a0","type":"paragraph","text":"徐：已经到了江心坡。","index":168,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"7a2d2d87e1","type":"paragraph","text":"周：他们出去时，护送部队同敌人打了一仗，他们安全过去了。","index":169,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"5a705d1b9d","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：带电台了吗？","index":170,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"811f61968d","type":"paragraph","text":"徐：带了。","index":171,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"e3c431a4db","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：你们也带电台吗？","index":172,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"0d51239f3a","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：带了。","index":173,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"3b69032681","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：要带电台。","index":174,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"667c1c1919","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：我们已经准备好了，现在就等下命令了。","index":175,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"e769430931","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：很好。","index":176,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"4705c962fa","type":"paragraph","text":"康：柯生同志他们急着要回去。","index":177,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"85e7721afe","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：赶快走！赶快走！","index":178,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"9fd3a9b490","type":"paragraph","text":"康：请柯生同志告诉大家，不会再留他们了。","index":179,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"db735446f2","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：不会留你们了。我们官僚主义，害得你们等了一个礼拜。","index":180,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"1212dba523","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：等一个礼拜不要紧。","index":181,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"aa6943f022","type":"paragraph","text":"周：最近敌情没有变化。","index":182,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"06aae53f35","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：你们还有什么问题没有？","index":183,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"57100911df","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：主要的问题是要回去。","index":184,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"8d9d380e81","type":"paragraph","text":"我向主席保证：第一，请主席放心，我们一定要打赢这场战争。第二，要是给我们分配有关国际方面的任务，我们保证完成。","index":185,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"24a962b407","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：刚才主席说可以动员中国境内的景颇族参加我们的部队，我非常高兴。我也有这个要求，同志们也有这个要求。","index":186,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"9f6b9e629c","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：你去找，找多少就带多少，找年轻的。","index":187,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"412656712d","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：我很高兴。中国境内的景颇族和缅甸境内的克钦族都是有联系的。","index":188,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"06b2307b3c","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：他们有义务帮助你们，这是他们的国际主义义务，但是你们要跟他们（指缅共）合作。","index":189,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"fbc9b67bd5","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：我们现在已经是缅甸共产党领导下的红军了。","index":190,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"fd64c1d09f","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：那就好。缅族是你们国家的一个大民族，这个民族不解放，你们小民族也不能得到解放。","index":191,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"06138cab3d","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：我们是在缅甸共产党领导下的队伍。","index":192,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"cf4be227db","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：那就好。","index":193,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"41bf260457","type":"paragraph","text":"康：他已经加入共产党了。","index":194,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"38451e9adb","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：那好。","index":195,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"984ab129e4","type":"paragraph","text":"周：最近还通过他去做克钦独立军的工作。","index":196,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"1bc6b33662","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：克钦独立军有你的部下嘛。","index":197,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"7518be08a3","type":"paragraph","text":"周：有些人过去是他的部下。","index":198,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"c16a15479f","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：吴努那时非常注意他（罗线）的部队，怕他的部队打回去。你在军队多久？","index":199,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"0586afcd11","type":"paragraph","text":"罗：有二十多年了，从打日本开始就在部队里了。","index":200,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"c346e53369","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：日本是什么时候占领缅甸的？","index":201,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"0648a53087","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：1942年占领缅甸，1945年被我们驱逐出去。","index":202,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"121d8246ed","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：1942年到1967年，已经25年了。吴努、奈温这些人是抗日时期开始参加政治活动的？","index":203,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"46396c60f8","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：吴努这个人没有参加抗日，他是日本的傀儡，是跟着日本人跑的。过去他访问中国的时候，中国报纸上说他参加过抗日，缅甸同志对这一条就不同意。1945年日本往缅甸南部撤的时候，他一直跟着日本人跑到边境。","index":204,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"c596766c61","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：这么个人。你刚才讲了两点。","index":205,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"a22401f727","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：第一点，请主席放心，缅甸共产党一定要用武装夺取政权。第二点，要是给我们国际上的任务，我们保证完成。","index":206,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"324157cfe5","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：什么意思？","index":207,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"fb3a2f526f","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：缅甸解放以后，还要支援泰国、马来亚、巴基斯坦、印度、印尼。最近泰共要求我们帮助他们，但那边还没有我们的人，准备派人过去。马共也要求缅共帮助他们送人到马来亚去，现在还做不到。","index":208,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"7f841463cf","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：由中国送人去还是由哪里送人去？","index":209,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"2057d93e02","type":"paragraph","text":"柯：从中国回去，经过缅甸，然后回到马来亚。","index":210,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"7a1a626ead","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：他们的人不多。","index":211,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"938a79a467","type":"paragraph","text":"刘宁一：干部40多人，侨民多一些。","index":212,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"fa14dab39f","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：最近几天马来亚有一个示威，因为英镑贬值，群众不满意，发生了示威。","index":213,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"},{"id":"dbf3177861","type":"paragraph","text":"就谈到这里。<br style=\"clear:both;\">","index":214,"publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea"}],"page":{"id":"3b57ec55d5","publicationId":"jimi","articleId":"fb8d181bea","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}